Award Title: CP1923-20 COVID-19 - Economic Impact Scenarios for South West of England Upper Tier areas
Award Description:
Devon County Council wishes to commission on behalf of South West Councils a set of economic 
scenarios that assess the impact of Covid-19. This is a one-off piece of economic modelling and requires the production of short interpretative reports for each of 15 South West Upper Tier Local Authority areas. The brief requires a range of potential economic recovery/re-set scenarios, associated durations and should draw national and other regional comparisons.
